name: Nina (Aoi) Sex Doll
description:
Embedding of Nina (aka Aoi) bestseller real sized silicone doll head produced by DSdoll (aka EXdoll) Chinese sex doll manufacturer. This head mostly compatible with DS145 (aka UT145, arte145) bodies. For training I chose close up SFW photos of Nina with reddish brown or black eyes and brunet or black wigs. Nina has very interesting and cute look with big eyes and very small nose. She is on half way between real person and anime character.

Embedding trained for 1000 steps on 'v1-5-pruned-emaonly' checkpoint, so it should works well with most of v1.5 forks and mixes. I used dataset of 48 images with 680x680 resolution, and learning rate: "0.05:10, 0.02:20, 0.01:60, 0.005:200, 0.002:500, 0.001". Personal likeness was reached at 30 steps. So probably embedding is over-trained.

If you want to force Nina to looks like a real person, I recommend to use this embedding with [ ] for reduce doll likeness. Also i recommend to use Realistic Glossy Face Skin LoRa by romixerr269 for enhancement of skin texture. In this case prompt may contain: "[AIDA_DSnina] as beautiful girl, pretty face, (rseemma:1.1) <lora:RSERomantic_RSESofiko_RSEEmma-v1:0.2>"

Purchasing "Embedding of Nina (Aoi) Sex Doll" on Ko-Fi for only 3$ you will achieve rights for selling images generated with it. Please contact me if you need some extended rights for sharing, selling, merging this embedding and so on.

Also on Ko-Fi you can support me and find some of my models, which are not published here.
